{
  "stem": "4670.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my dad, who had a very good position, we were considered wealthy, and they probably looked us over and decided that if we were coming to the United States, they would have to give us this kind of life, which was very foolish, because we were not looking to be supported.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't think any Jewish refugee looked for that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that was the reason.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I believe that was their reason.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, also, one of the reasons, which was not their fault, the quotas, unfortunately, were extremely small.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I fault President Roosevelt for that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The quotas were so small that many, many people would have been saved if they hadn't had that particular-- that these quotas were so little.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We finally, in 19-- it went on until-- until we got the papers and everything.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My sister, Renata, she left first.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She left for the United States.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And since she was already-- by that time, she was 23-- she could go by herself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she had her own passport, she came first.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then, my sister Margot, who had a fiance at that time, she came with her fiance.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She left about a couple months before we did.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And Papi, Mutti, and I, we went to the embassy in Stuttgart.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You had to-- before you came to the United States, you had to visit a doctor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That was very important because the rules, health rules, in the United States are you cannot have an eye disease or you cannot have a lung disease.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It was very important.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Unfortunately, I caught pneumonia and I was in the hospital in August of 1938.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And when I came out of the hospital, of course, there's always a little shadow on your lung.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I didn't even think about it until we went to Stuttgart.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
